Claud Allister https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Claud_Allister 0 Claud Allister (born William Claud Michael Palmer, 3 October 1888 – 26 July 1970) was an English actor with an extensive film career in Hollywood, where he appeared in more than 70 films between 1929 and 1955.
